& [SLMPrimerCompactionBudgetContract] is the contract for bounded compact evidence in SLM primers
  + [contract_uuid] is 9e134f29-3d81-48f6-8adf-0e027969a16f
  + [slice_id] is SLM-37
  + [depends_on] is SLM_Primer_Rendering_Contract, SLM_Lexical_Sense_Evidence_Contract, SLM_Primer_Provider_Evidence_Contract
  + [status] is verified_wsl

  & [Purpose] is to keep primer evidence machine-reingestible as the evidence workspace grows
    = must: preserve compact evidence required to reconstruct the reasoning surface
    = must: cap verbose evidence classes before they dominate the primer
    = must: rank capped evidence by support activation and stable id ordering
    = must: report omitted evidence counts by kind
    = must: keep compaction policy visible in the primer JSON
    - never: use compaction to hide unresolved uncertainty, contradiction, or wobble

  & [MustKeepEvidenceKinds] are evidence classes retained as routing-critical
    + [kind] is tokens
    + [kind] is structural_hint
    + [kind] is span_candidate
    + [kind] is contradiction
    + [kind] is provider_deliberation
    + [kind] is wobble

  & [CappedEvidenceKinds] are evidence classes with v0 top-k budgets
    + [support] is top support records by support_activation
    + [provider_suggestion] is top provider suggestions by support_activation then stable id
    + [lexical_sense] is top senses per token by support_activation then stable id
    = must: keep at least lexical sense evidence for open-class terms when available
    = must: treat closed-class sense deferral from SLM-38 as upstream evidence routing rather than primer-only filtering

  & [RuntimeProjection] is the Rust source surface
    + [module] is slm_rust/src/primer.rs PrimerCompactionBudget
    + [module] is slm_rust/src/primer.rs PrimerCompactionSummary
    + [module] is slm_rust/src/primer.rs compact_evidence_with_budget
    + [proof_route] is WSL cargo test and demo primer evidence-kind inspection

  ! [Slice37SourceComplete] is accepted
    @ [source_gate] passed python slm_project/tools/slm_source_gate_check.py
    @ [wsl_cargo_test] passed 9 tests through CARGO_TARGET_DIR=/home/pinky/slm_rust_target and linker=/home/pinky/bin/zigcc
    @ [self_check] passed slm_self_check
    @ [demo_proof] workspace lexical sense candidates were 13 and primer retained 6 lexical_sense compact evidence items
    @ [demo_proof] primer compaction reported 37 omitted evidence items by kind
